name: Starstorm Lost
description:
Starstorm survivors that lost the poll, now finished up. 
Currently implements four survivors and two variants. 

     Profile Flags: 

- ssl_truebrawler: Enables Brawler's true potential, including 7 additional moves executed via fighting-game style inputs. 
- ssl_debug: Enables several debug features, mainly a display of Brawler's input systems. 
- ssl_heckbosses: Brawler can suplex any enemy.
